{{Quote|<nowiki></nowiki>''Skywalker...'' I sense your presence... How did you get in here? The clone lab is ''sealed''... My moment of transference is close... No one is ''allowed'' in here now.|[[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]], to [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]]|<ref name="Dark Empire 5">[[Dark Empire 5|''Dark Empire'' 5]]</ref>}}
The '''Clone Labs''', also known as '''Clone Lab complex''' were the area of the [[Emperor's Citadel]] on [[Byss/Legends|Byss]] that contained [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine's]] [[Cloning tank|clone vats]]. They were overseen by the [[Clone Keeper]], the [[Constable of Homunculi]].<ref name="DES" />

